1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b319503044348c62633b2e0db0ddc6cf3a6b8ccb","tid":1593181,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T12:59:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T13:33:09.000Z","msg":"最近不停有TG/Global的人叫我地搞29/9 anti chinazi/anti totalitarian 活動，我地講明唔會搞，但日日chur我地，宜家仲有人以遊客身分過黎，再搵韓國有名NGO搞，好彩人地問一問我地咩事，我地解釋問題所在，個NGO都決定唔搞。<br />\n<br />\n第一 系你老母<br />\n<br />\n第二 即係你放暗箭割蓆仲要叫人地NGO唔好幫手？<br />\n個活動本身有咩問題？<br />\n普世價值嘅活動嚟<br />\n你話佢地戇鳩邀請過藍絲一齊<br />\n<br />\n即係我寄invitation 俾美國共和黨就唔俾得民主黨？<br />\n佢地對立成日想攻擊對方喎<br />\n<br />\n點得出俾人利用呢個結論<br />\n<br />\n你論點唔清釋喎<br />\n仲有你啲用字自撚大到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03befae5f2f8b8a633a19fc6745abe1e9f7298aa","tid":1593181,"uid":213893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b319503044348c62633b2e0db0ddc6cf3a6b8ccb","tid":1593181,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T12:59:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T13:33:47.000Z","msg":"Sorry 覆錯人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想覆樓主"},{"pid":"630ba0eed9dc1350fd677d3525fc0dcb4a2a28ed","tid":1593181,"uid":7278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T13:38:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"272744b35ed7f66b9741d699f67d34222d9d342d","tid":1593181,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T13:39:04.000Z","msg":"樓主朋友有冇時間再講多d韓國政局？<br />\n點解佢地既國民可以自己選總統選議員，但偏偏個政府政黨就唔支持民主自由？定係我理解錯？"},{"pid":"b1a4af890b1e2c23fa284d75c7908e